data.description: No Flooding!!! This home is a must see! Beautiful 4 bedroom home on a large corner lot and cul-de-sac. Home has so many upgrades. PEX Plumbing, Tankless Water Heater, Double Pane Windows, HVAC 2020, Cabinets and Fixtures, Plantation Shutters throughout. No Carpet!!! Oversized extended covered patio. Enter through a gated courtyard and into a ranch style layout. Spacious updated kitchen with granite countertops, island with cooktop, custom cabinets and fabulous fixtures. Study doors are a stunning centerpiece of the home. Beautiful vinyl flooring in rooms. Primary suite with remodeled bathroom, double vanity, 2 walk-in closets. Relax on your extended covered patio with outdoor TV and setup for an outdoor kitchen. Low maintenance yard with shed. Home is located in highly Sought out Greentree subdivision. Near greenbelt trails, shopping, schools and easy access to W. Lake Houston Pkwy, Kingwood Dr and North Park. Check out the upgrade list in the photos.
